Plan a Vacation
1.	Decide where you want to go
2.	Create a list of activities that you would like to do
3.	Find out when is the best time to go to that location to do the activities you want to do
4.	Define how much time do you need to perform the activities you want to do
5.	If you need to ask for vacation at work, communicate the dates and confirm vacation time
6.	Research the different costs: Transportation, Accommodation, Food and Activities
7.	Create a budget 
8.	Make reservations (Transportation, Accommodation, Food and Activities)
9.	Create a packing list
10.	Buy the items you donâ€™t own yet from the packing list
11.	Pack
12.	Go on Vacation
